---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Direct Invest Group | Who Is Abebe?">

  <Header>
    <Fragment slot="title">Direct Invest Group</Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      A source-code and Wayback Machine trail connecting archived Direct Invest material
      to Mike Abebe, Carlton Brown, and related development records.
    </Fragment>
  </Header>

  <main class="article-wrap">
    <article class="article-body report-page">

      <p class="lede">
        This report documents how the Direct Invest Group connection was identified:
        first through source-code/source-reference review, then through an archived
        Wayback Machine capture showing Mike Abebe listed in Direct Invest partner material.
      </p>

      <div class="notice-box">
        <strong>Scope:</strong>
        This page summarizes public-facing archived web material and captured screenshots.
        It does not claim private knowledge of any ownership, financing, or internal relationship.
      </div>

      <h2>Archived Direct Invest Link</h2>

      <p>
        The key archived source is the
        <a
          href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210414134021/https://www.directinvestdevelopment.com/studio"
          target="_blank"
        >Direct Invest Development studio page</a>
        preserved by the Wayback Machine.
      </p>

      <a
        class="document-row"
        href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210414134021/https://www.directinvestdevelopment.com/studio"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <span>Wayback Capture</span>
        <strong>Direct Invest Development Studio</strong>
        <p>Archived April 14, 2021 by the Internet Archive Wayback Machine.</p>
      </a>

      <h2>Source-Code Discovery</h2>

      <p>
        The research trail began with a source-code/source-reference capture
        where the Direct Invest site material exposed a Mike Abebe reference.
        That source clue was then compared against the archived public page.
      </p>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/entities/mike-abebe-direct-invest-source-reference.png"
          alt="Source-code screenshot showing Mike Abebe reference in Direct Invest material"
        />
        <figcaption>Captured source/reference evidence showing the Mike Abebe discovery path.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Wayback Partner Evidence</h2>

      <p>
        The
        <a
          href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210414134021/https://www.directinvestdevelopment.com/studio"
          target="_blank"
        >archived Direct Invest page</a>
        shows Mike Abebe in partner material
        alongside Carlton Brown and Gizman Abbas. This is the public-facing
        source that ties the name reference back to an archived Direct Invest page.
      </p>

      <div class="notice-box">
        <strong>Current-site update:</strong>
        The live Abebe Ventures leadership page now uses a newer Mike Abebe
        headshot and publishes a fuller company biography. That current profile
        helps place the older Direct Invest Wayback/source-code evidence in the
        broader Abebe Ventures identity trail.
        <a href="https://www.abebe.com/leadership" target="_blank">Open Abebe.com leadership page</a>.
      </div>

      <figure class="report-figure">
        <img
          src="/images/entities/direct-invest-wayback-mike-abebe-partner.png"
          alt="Wayback screenshot showing Carlton Brown, Mike Abebe, and Gizman Abbas in Direct Invest partner material"
        />
        <figcaption>
          Wayback capture showing Carlton Brown, Mike Abebe, and Gizman Abbas in Direct Invest partner material.
          <a
            href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210414134021/https://www.directinvestdevelopment.com/studio"
            target="_blank"
          >Open archived source</a>.
        </figcaption>
      </figure>

      <h2>Working Interpretation</h2>

      <div class="fact-grid">
        <div class="fact-card">
          <span>Verified</span>
          <p>
            The archive contains a source/reference screenshot and a Wayback
            capture that show Mike Abebe connected to Direct Invest public web material.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fact-card">
          <span>Observation</span>
          <p>
            The Direct Invest archived page places Mike Abebe in the same partner
            context as Carlton Brown and Gizman Abbas.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fact-card">
          <span>Open Question</span>
          <p>
            Further documentation is needed to define the exact business structure,
            duration, and legal relationship between Direct Invest and other entities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Bridge to Elysian Development Group</h2>

      <p>
        Carlton Brown is the key bridge into the Elysian Development Group thread.
        In the archived Direct Invest material, Carlton Brown appears alongside
        Mike Abebe. In the Elysian Development Group advisor material captured
        in this archive, Carlton Brown appears again in an advisor context.
      </p>

      <a class="section-card feature-card" href="/reports/elysian-development-group">
        <span>Connected Report</span>
        <h3>Elysian Development Group</h3>
        <p>
          Review the captured Elysian advisor material and the Carlton Brown
          connection from Direct Invest into the Elysian development record.
        </p>
      </a>

    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />

</BaseLayout>
